reviewText: This is a video for both boys and girls and it is both entertainingand educational. When I went to the supermarket, I had never thought of where the food comes from, now I do. Thanks, Annie, for a great video!

This is an absolutely fabulous video that is both entertaining and educational.  The charming hostess introduces children to the fascinating world of the farm.  Lively paced and lots of fun, it's great video for all  members of the family.  It is one of the best of the videos that Annie has  produced.
